China Fund Allows Bets on Government Policy, Morning Post Says

-- B y   T o m   K o h n
-- 
2011-02-20T02:35:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-20/china-fund-allows-bets-on-government-policy-morning-post-says.html
A fund is letting investors bet on
Chinese government policy, showing how state capitalism may be
defying market wisdom, the  South China Morning Post  reported,
citing material promoting the fund.  China Construction Bank International’s China Policy Driven
Fund targets mainland investors in Hong Kong and will “follow
the policies,” rather than “follow the money,” the newspaper
said in its Sunday edition today.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tom Kohn at 
 tkohn@bloomberg.net  